column5: Got my Passports today after 6 wks. Just in time for our July trip.  Did you get yours in time or was it too late?
PASSPORTS???....  PASSPORTS???...  We don't need no stinking PASSPORTS!!!
Right, no passports.  We want a parole.
Well when ya have as thick of a southern accent as I have... where the hell else are ya gonna be from... Yemen???
Got mine in November so I wouldn't get stuck in the mad rush to get one!
we also applied for ours in November at the hamilton office, it took 11 days couriered to our door
Article about them in the paper here today also, they are running behind processing them. Go figure!
Is that the U.S. or Canadian passport office in the paper Paul?
I thought you only needed passports if you are flying into canada??
US Nanook, I think you only need one for flying in to the country this year, next year for driving too?

U.S. Citizens just need a raised seal birth certificate until January 1, 2008. If flying into Canada you do need a passport effective NOW. I am going to get my passport so I don't have to worry about it!
